This is a bunch of user styles and scripts to improve beluga integration using fluid.

== Basic Instructions

  1. Copy the content of style.css into your userstyles
  2. Copy the content of dist.js into your userscripts
  
== Features

  * Pretty interface
  * cmd+enter to post
  * Growl notifications
  * Notification count in dock

== Build Instructions

If you want to modify it and build it yourself:

  * Install CoffeeScript http://jashkenas.github.com/coffee-script/
  * Run build.sh
  
Note: You don't need to build it to use it, just copy the existing contents.